1.00	Jay_Hunt_(stylist)	Jay Hunt (stylist)	Jay Hunt (born 1965) is the managing director of Violet Productions a London based video production company. She has previously worked as a celebrity stylist, personal shopper and TV presenter/producer. She worked in television since 1990, and was a presenter of the dating show Would Like To Meet, dieting show Do Or Diet was the resident style presenter on Housecalls. She co-wrote the series-accompanying book Would Like to Meet: The Ultimate Dating Makeover in 2002.	
